data.description: Nestled within the sought-after Ladera master-planned community, this exquisite two-story home offers modern luxury living, situated on a premium lot that provides privacy and breathtaking Hill Country views. In the heart of the home, the open-concept main level beckons, with soaring ceilings that create a sense of grandeur, and a modern kitchen adorned with the latest painted cabinetry, sleek quartz countertops, and SS appliances. Natural light abounds, accentuated by contemporary light fixtures and recessed lighting that infuses the space with an inviting ambiance. The main level owner's suite is a true sanctuary, featuring a sizable walk-in closet that connects to the laundry room, and an ensuite bath that exudes elegance, showcasing a dual vanity separated by a makeup counter and a generously sized walk-in shower equipped with a soothing rain shower head. A second bedroom downstairs provides versatility for guests or family members, while the remaining bedrooms are set upstairs with a sprawling bonus living space, providing you with an ideal setup for separation from the owner's suite. With a versatile den, two living spaces, and a total of four bathrooms, this home exudes convenience and comfort. Step outside to discover a raised back patio that provides abundant room for both grilling and lounging. Elevated for unobstructed views of the lush greenery that extends beyond the expansive backyard, this outdoor space promises tranquility. The Ladera community offers an array of outstanding amenities and an Elementary School within its bounds. Positioned just off 211, this home enjoys quick access to Potranco Rd, ensuring you're moments away from essential destinations such as HEB, Shops at Dove Creek, Alamo Ranch Shopping Center, and the Golf Club of Texas. This residence isn't just a home; it's a haven of contemporary elegance, thoughtful design, and convenient living. Come and experience modern luxury in the heart of Ladera's coveted master-planned community.
